'''Black Knights''', also known as the '''[[Kinshra]]''', are [[human]] warriors found mainly in their [[Black Knights' Fortress (location)|fortress]] and [[Black_Knights'_Base|stronghold]]. They are central to the [[Black Knights' Fortress]] [[Quests|quest]].

Once [[Wanted!]] has been completed, Black Knights can be slain in order to raise the player's [[White equipment#Knight Rankings|White Knight rank]]. As their rank gets higher, they can purchase more [[white equipment]]. Even though the quest, as well as White Knight armour, are only for members, non-members are able to increase their rank.

