==Trivia==
*Black Knights are some of the oldest [[non-player character]]s in ''RuneScape''. When the game was first released, Black Knights were the strongest foes at level 46, and only three of them existed.
*Killing the [[Black knight (Port Sarim Jail)|Black knight]] found in the [[Port Sarim Jail]] will not contribute to the player's White Knight rank.
*Despite only being useful for members, free-to-play players can increase their White Knight rank if they have [[Wanted!]] completed.
*Ironically enough, despite the fact that the Black Knights appear to wear [[Black equipment]], they are incapable of dropping it.

